### ============================================
### 🛍️ TEST API PRODUCTS - SuperMarketMini
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = 
@managerToken = 
@warehouseToken = 
@cashierToken = 

### ============================================
### 🔐 1. LOGIN - Lấy Token
### ============================================

### 1.1 Login Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 1.2 Login Manager (đã tạo từ trước)
# @name loginManager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testmanager",
  "password": "Test@123"
}

### 1.3 Login Warehouse (đã tạo từ trước)
# @name loginWarehouse
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testwarehouse",
  "password": "Test@123"
}

### 1.4 Login Cashier (đã tạo từ trước)
# @name loginCashier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testcashier",
  "password": "Test@123"
}

### ============================================
### 📝 2. CREATE USERS (Chỉ chạy 1 lần đầu)
### ============================================

### 2.1 Register Manager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test Manager",
  "username": "testmanager",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "confirmPassword": "Test@123",
  "role": "Manager"
}

### 2.2 Register Warehouse
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test Warehouse",
  "username": "testwarehouse",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "confirmPassword": "Test@123",
  "role": "Warehouse"
}

### 2.3 Register Cashier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test Cashier",
  "username": "testcashier",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "confirmPassword": "Test@123",
  "role": "Cashier"
}

### ============================================
### 📦 3. CRUD PRODUCTS - ADMIN
### ============================================

### 3.1 Get All Products (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3.2 Get Product By ID (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3.3 Create Product (Admin) - SUCCESS
# @name createProductAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Admin Product Test",
  "description": "Product created by admin",
  "sellPrice": 25000,
  "costPrice": 18000,
  "unit": "hộp",
  "barcode": "ADMIN_TEST_001",
  "minQuantity": 10,
  "maxQuantity": 200
}

### 3.4 Update Product (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Updated Product Name",
  "sellPrice": 30000,
  "isActive": true
}

### 3.5 Delete Product (Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

